as untrustworthy.

00:19:53.890 --> 00:19:57.320
After a few months, the
relationship partners

00:19:57.320 --> 00:20:00.890
of narcissists report being
enormously dissatisfied.

00:20:00.890 --> 00:20:04.780
It works very well up front,
not so well in the long term.

00:20:04.780 --> 00:20:06.410
And across the
board, you see this

00:20:06.410 --> 00:20:07.660
with a lot of negative traits.

00:20:07.660 --> 00:20:09.910
Short-term effectiveness,
long term not so much.

00:20:09.910 --> 00:20:13.434
If you're a used car dealer,
it might be a fantastic choice.

00:20:13.434 --> 00:20:15.100
But if you're working
in an organization

00:20:15.100 --> 00:20:17.516
that you plan on being for a
number of years, probably not

00:20:17.516 --> 00:20:19.150
a good idea.

