confident in there

00:24:12.570 --> 00:24:13.710
but utterly deluded.

00:24:13.710 --> 00:24:15.300
And I use that
story to illustrate

00:24:15.300 --> 00:24:17.580
the issue of confidence.

00:24:17.580 --> 00:24:20.155
We talk about confidence
like it's this panacea.

00:24:20.155 --> 00:24:21.280
You got to have confidence.

00:24:21.280 --> 00:24:22.470
You can't be lack of confidence.

00:24:22.470 --> 00:24:23.910
And there are downsides
to confidence.

00:24:23.910 --> 00:24:25.743
When you take confidence
out to the extreme,

00:24:25.743 --> 00:24:26.790
it can be delusional.

00:24:26.790 --> 00:24:28.740
It can lead to
narcissism or hubris.

00:24:28.740 --> 00:24:31.960
You know confidence isn't
the answer to everything.

00:24:31.960 --> 00:24:36.047
And I use that to illustrate
when confidence goes too far.

00:24:36.047 --> 00:24:38.130
