00:25:09.660 --> 00:25:10.860
SPEAKER 1: Fantastic.

00:25:10.860 --> 00:25:14.340
I'm going to go to some
audience questions now.

00:25:14.340 --> 00:25:17.070
Nassim Taleb wrote,
success isn't being on top

00:25:17.070 --> 00:25:17.920
of a hierarchy.

00:25:17.920 --> 00:25:20.340
It's standing outside
