that I have any opportunity.

00:26:54.499 --> 00:26:55.790
Bad things are going to happen.

00:26:55.790 --> 00:26:57.998
I'm not going to be thrilled
about them all the time.

00:26:57.998 --> 00:26:59.900
But I'm lucky to be here at all.

00:26:59.900 --> 00:27:02.090
And that's something
we can all learn

00:27:02.090 --> 00:27:04.360
from in terms of happiness.

00:27:04.360 --> 00:27:06.622
SPEAKER 1: That's
a really good idea.

00:27:06.622 --> 00:27:08.330
