for the first 10 years

00:34:50.659 --> 00:34:52.250
and then make up for it.

00:34:52.250 --> 00:34:53.150
That doesn't work.

00:34:53.150 --> 00:34:56.110
So people need to balance
happiness, achievement,

00:34:56.110 --> 00:34:57.180
significance, and legacy.

