00:38:53.170 --> 00:38:55.510
circles, said that
a great leader

00:38:55.510 --> 00:38:58.660
has to have people around him
who will be honest with him,

00:38:58.660 --> 00:38:59.830
who he can trust.

00:38:59.830 --> 00:39:03.910
Because otherwise you're
going to spin out of control.

00:39:03.910 --> 00:39:05.950
You need people who
will be honest with you.

00:39:05.950 --> 00:39:07.690
But past that,
something you can do--

00:39:07.690 --> 00:39:09.610
Peter Drucker, one of
the leading management

00:39:09.610 --> 00:39:11.080
