00:39:25.220 --> 00:39:28.300
And then you can start to
get an idea over time--

00:39:28.300 --> 00:39:30.850
how accurate am I?

00:39:30.850 --> 00:39:33.850
Because that's the problem
with too much confidence

00:39:33.850 --> 00:39:36.070
is the issue of delusion,
where you're not

00:39:36.070 --> 00:39:37.760
in touch with reality anymore.

00:39:37.760 --> 00:39:39.730
