00:39:43.390 --> 00:39:45.160
You are or you aren't.

00:39:45.160 --> 00:39:47.370
And that's where
overconfidence gets you killed.

00:39:47.370 --> 00:39:50.680
But there's usually not such
an obvious corrective mechanism

00:39:50.680 --> 00:39:54.111
