mostly written by armchair

00:49:32.300 --> 00:49:35.090
plagiarists quoting
each other, and doing

00:49:35.090 --> 00:49:37.340
a lot of scientific research.

00:49:37.340 --> 00:49:39.140
But the scientific
research was always

00:49:39.140 --> 00:49:43.279
with slightly above
