00:49:45.820 --> 00:49:46.850
It's really hard.

00:49:46.850 --> 00:49:49.750
Say, hey, I'm going to follow
you around with videotape.

00:49:49.750 --> 00:49:51.410
But I did that.

00:49:51.410 --> 00:49:54.910
And I was blown away
that in sales, at least,

