00:50:14.000 --> 00:50:15.920
I'm happy, I'm always happy.

00:50:15.920 --> 00:50:18.620
I'm living in this cardboard
box, but I'm happy.

00:50:18.620 --> 00:50:23.540
So I was completely shocked
