00:50:27.020 --> 00:50:31.610
here, because you said
that everything that's

00:50:31.610 --> 00:50:36.510
contrary to what you
normally hear in science.

00:50:36.510 --> 00:50:39.367
And so what these
people would do--

00:50:39.367 --> 00:50:40.950
and they're number
one in their field.

00:50:40.950 --> 00:50:43.000
One of them is number
one in life insurance.

00:50:43.000 --> 00:50:45.590
He'd sell $4.5 million
selling two days a week.

00:50:45.590 --> 00:50:48.980
